{"tid":1410950,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"被藍絲打應該點做？","createTime":"2019-08-05T02:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T04:58:24.000Z","uid":250586,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6c29947eac5f952f89de2e0f050fd01c1a4aed72","tid":1410950,"uid":250586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:43:13.000Z","msg":"經歷過大量風風雨雨之後，今早見到有柒頭係柴灣俾藍絲打依然堅持報警，然後無差佬理佢（其實預左）。<br />\n<br />\n我自己認為被藍絲打：<br />\n<br />\n一係走<br />\n二係還手<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但千萬不要報警！你咁做等如幫對家吹雞幫手打你！</span><br />\n<br />\n但似乎唔係人人認同，小弟愚昧，想在這裡請教大家為甚麼要報警？有甚麼後著？還是有甚麼妙計可以指教一下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c040413edda6b863dbbd446b85c9fdc5ae86fc9f","tid":1410950,"uid":250586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:43:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2046ee0b07f8eff0b5b31990272b057e49c0033d","tid":1410950,"uid":49366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:45:18.000Z","msg":"還手for sure"},{"pid":"35fc0e3fca299f9e29f8a978628230b1ab261e4c","tid":1410950,"uid":250586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:45:18.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4f04f011148790164ec4010e5aa8214464ed79b4","tid":1410950,"uid":250586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:46:30.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"cd1232cbfb4e352d6735e814e9e2ba314502d458","tid":1410950,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:46:55.000Z","msg":"以直報怨<br />\nAn eye for an eye"},{"pid":"e78b54f3b7a189eb1b5366e2834a311ce9448610","tid":1410950,"uid":250586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:49:07.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e7229c4847023c13b93c3fdb1048b8c70156aa3c","tid":1410950,"uid":250586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:50:42.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n求堅持報警人士賜教<img src=\